# makefile for CQL3D using lf95 for mpi version on bob5
# Nikolay Ershov, Jan. 14, 2006
# This makefile has been adjusted from makefile_lf95 to parallelize
# the solution of the Fokker-Planck equation over radial flux
# surfaces.  The ./mpi/doparallel.py python script is used
# along with ancilliary files in ./mpi, and the file mpilib.f.

# LIBRARIES in makefile_lf95 had to be specifically adjusted for
# for the mpi version. [I believe Ershov found that libraries for
# pgplot, blas, and lapack had to be compiled with lf95, rather
# than using Suse provided libraries, to remove a runtime error. 
# BH, 2006].

SHELL     = /bin/sh
NAME      = cqlp
INCLUDES  = advnce.h comm.h frcomm.h frname.h frname_decl.h name.h param.h trans.h wpadvnc.h  \
	name_decl.h
SOURCES  = a_cqlp.f  abchief.f  achief1.f  achiefn.f  aclear.f  ainalloc.f  \
	aindflt.f  aindflt1.f aindfpa.f  aingeom.f  ainitial.f   \
